      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, this beauty is something special. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed with love. It honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor; the ride is smooth as silk and it still has that fresh, clean feel inside. You might find a tiny, microscopic mark if you really go hunting, but to me, she\u2019s pure perfection. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Swing by, let's chat cars, and take her for a spin!",
