      "description": "This isn't just a driver; it's a meticulously sorted specimen for the discerning enthusiast. The powerplant features a broad, linear torque curve thanks to a precision-calibrated ECU map and optimized airflow via a high-flow intake plenum. We\u2019ve refreshed the entire subframe with stiffened bushings to sharpen turn-in response, while the active dampers have been re-valved for a more communicative chassis feel. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing zero signs of heat cycling or track fatigue. Every fluid swap\u2014from the transaxle to the differential\u2014has been executed at half-intervals using high-shear synthetics. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine with a zero-compromise maintenance history. If you're looking for a factory-plus feel with visceral engagement, this is the benchmark.",
